== Description ==
[[File:DoomworldHereticSpeed02.png|thumb|Convection, schmonvection.]]
The '''Doomworld Heretic Speedmapping Sessions''', spearheaded by Walter Confalonieri, are an ongoing series of map packs for Heretic and ZDoom. Similarly to the {{dw|32in24}}, participants have 24 hours to create and submit their entries. The quality of the maps therefore varies wildly, but they all tend to have a simple layout and a simple, straightforward gameplay, with few traps and ambushes.

Session 1 offers five maps designed for single player mode. Sessions 2 and 3, lumped together, offer a mix of deathmatch and duel maps. Session 4, meant for Skulltag, offers three "Capture the Flag" maps.

